data.Name: Aqueous
data.Bio: If you're looking for the Avant-garde band from New Jersey, go to "aqueouss" Aqueous is a jam band from Buffalo, NY. Often compared to the likes of other jam band heavyweights moe., Phish, and Umphrey's McGee, as well as 70's prog-rock, Aqueous is a band that pushes onward and upward with every performance, live and in the studio. Playing over 100 shows since their formation in early 2006. Aqueous has graced the stage of many notable venues, and with their ever growing dedicated fan base, the venues have gotten bigger and better. Read more on Last.fm
